FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our Ethereum transaction finder app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to find and track new Ethereum transactions in real-time, providing you with up-to-date information on the Ethereum blockchain.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How quickly does the app update with new transactions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: The app updates in near real-time, typically within seconds of a new transaction being broadcast to the Ethereum network.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I filter transactions by specific criteria?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, you can filter transactions by various parameters such as wallet address, transaction value, gas price, and more, allowing you to focus on the information that matters most to you.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is this app suitable for both beginners and experienced Ethereum users?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app is designed with an intuitive interface for beginners, while also offering advanced features for experienced users and developers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How secure is the app when accessing Ethereum transaction data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We prioritize security and privacy. The app uses read-only access to the Ethereum blockchain, ensuring that your personal information and assets remain safe while you explore transaction data.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is EthScan and how does it work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: EthScan is a powerful app designed to help you discover and track new Ethereum transactions in real-time. It connects directly to the Ethereum blockchain, constantly monitoring for new transactions and presenting them to you in an easy-to-understand format.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can EthScan notify me about specific types of transactions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, EthScan offers customizable alerts. You can set up notifications for transactions involving specific addresses, smart contracts, or even transactions exceeding a certain ETH value. This feature ensures you never miss important blockchain activity.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is EthScan suitable for both beginners and advanced users?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! EthScan is designed with an intuitive interface for newcomers to easily track Ethereum transactions. For advanced users, we offer additional features like detailed transaction analysis, gas fee tracking, and integration with popular wallets and DApps.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How up-to-date is the transaction data in EthScan?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: EthScan provides near real-time updates. Our app typically detects new transactions within seconds of them being broadcast to the Ethereum network. This ensures you have the most current information available for your crypto activities and research.
